@redwolfe98 Hi. It seems caused by `Dandelion Sprout's Annoyances List`.
Please test in user rules:
`ghacks.net#@##comments`

I can reproduce. These rules seem working for me

```adblock
x.com#$#div[role="group"] > div[style]:not([class]):has(> div[class] > div[class] > a[href^="https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/"]) { display: none !important; }
x.com#$#div[role="group"] > div[data-testid="mask"] { display: none !important; }
x.com#$#html[style] { overflow: auto !important; position: static !important; }
```
